 limited manual dexterity), \no  emotional/cognitive/behavioral impairments (for example, memory deficits, impaired judgment, fear), \no  sensory impairments (for example, impaired vision, pain), \no  environmental barriers (for example, access to kitchen or medication storage area, stairs, narrow \n\ndoorways). \n\n\u2022", "type": "Document"}}